  "original_title": "\u0b86\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Students who do not care about risk",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the lack of buses to go to school, students have to go to school in trucks.",
        "Students studying at Mahawa Palalla Navodaya School and Vijayapathiya School have been waiting on the road for hours for a bus when a truck traveling on the road helped the students.",
        "It is noteworthy that more and more students traveled in this truck with the idea of \u200b\u200bgoing to school somehow despite the danger."
      ],
